      "raw_text": "The Electrical Workers union\nhas procured legal advice and may\nsecure warrants for the officers OF\nthe Washington Water Power Co\non account of the alleged disregard\nby that corporation of the state\nlaw requiring the use of safety\nbrake appliances on passenger cars\nThe electrical workers claim that\nthe lives of passengers on the Medi-\ncal Lake line are endangered by\nnoncompliance with the law in re-\ngard to brakes."
